name: NeutrophilCount
title: Neutrophil count
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains lab tests commonly used for a blood neutrophil lab test using a #/volume measurement.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have had a laboratory test for a neutrophil count.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the "Laboratory test, performed datatype.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include codes representing neutrophil count using the LOINC code system.),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
